 Pure Hidden is unlike any other Hidden Object game you have ever played.
 It's bigger, better and more beautiful. Each of the 30 hidden objects areas
 is a work of art, with every single object (1,001 in total) skilfully
 hidden.

 Instead of searching in dark dungeons and dusty tombs, Pure Hidden has a
 huge array of different scenarios: comic books, black and white films,
 casinos, maps, sweet shops - it's unlike anything you've ever seen before.

 As if that were not enough, Pure Hidden also gives you 36 minigame levels
 in between - some just for fun, some plain daft and some fiendishly tricky!
 Wacky jigsaws, Rock, Paper, Scissors and a device that puts that 'cat' in
 'catapult' are just some of the delights that await.
